). Uncorrected pairwise genetic distances (p-distances, 

) were computed in MEGA version 5.2 to delineate the new species from their congeneric sister taxon using mt COI gene data. Maximum Likelihood (ML) tree was generated using raxmlGUI v1.3 (
Silvestro & Michalak 2012
). The ML tree was obtained with 1000 thorough bootstrap replicates under GTR+GAMMA+I model. The RaxML output tree was viewed using FigTree v1.4.0 (

) with 
Odontotermes
as outgroup (

Amina 
